it Only populated if Affordability is requested. Sum of the Monthly payment of all SP active revolving CAIS accounts excl. mortgages. Where the CAIS supplied monthly payment is 0, the payment is estimated using the following: CAIS account type 8  Balance / 12 All other account types Balance / 24 Max Value 999999", "offset": "Commitments", "format": "Num (7)"}, {"reference": "SP-H-40,SPA-H-40", "reference_concat": "sph40,spah40", "type of data": "SP,SPA", "description": "Monthly Credit Commitments - Non-Revolving Credit Only populated if Affordability is requested. Sum of the Monthly payments of all SP active non-revolving CAIS accounts excl. mortgages and current accounts. Where the CAIS supplied monthly payment is 0, the payment is estimated using the following: CAIS account type 19 Balance / Term If Term=0 Balance / 36 All other account types The lesser of: 1000 and Balance / MAX (3, Term - Months Run) If Term=0 then Balance / 36 Max value 999999", "offset": "Commitments", "format": "Num (7)"}, {"reference": "SP-H-41,SPA-H-41", "reference_concat": "sph41,spah41", "type of data": "SP,SPA", "description": "Monthly Mortgage Payment Only populated if Affordability is requested. (Sum of the Monthly payments of all SP active CAIS mortgage and secured loan accounts \u00e2\u20ac\u201c uses an algorithm to estimate this value if the Monthly payment on the CAIS record is 0). Max Value 999999", "offset": "Commitments", "format": "Num (7)"}, {"reference": "SP-I-42", "reference_concat": "spi42", "type of data": "SP & SPA", "description": "Total Unsecured Balance as a % of Gross Annual Income (Banded) Only populated if ECII is requested. Banded version of SP-I-44", "offset": "Income Ratio (Banded Unsecured)", "format": "Num (4)"}, {"reference": "SP-I-43", "reference_concat": "spi43", "type of data": "SP & SPA", "description": "Total Secured Balance as a % of Gross Annual Income (Banded) Only populated if ECII is requested. Banded version of SP-I-45", "offset": "Income Ratio (Banded Secured)", "format": "Num (4)"}, {"reference": "SP-I-44", "reference_concat": "spi44", "type of data": "SP & SPA", "description": "Total Unsecured Balance as a % of Gross Annual Income Only populated if Income Estimation and Verification package is requested. (SP) Balance of all active CAIS, excluding mortgages divided by Gross Annual Income (SP-I-46) x 100", "offset": "Income Ratio", "format": "Num (4)"}, {"reference": "SP-I-45", "reference_concat": "spi45", "type of data": "SP & SPA", "description": "Total Secured Balance as a % of Gross Annual Income Only populated if Income Estimation and Verification package is requested. (SP) Total outstanding Balance on Mortgages / Gross Annual Income (SP-I-46) x 100", "offset": "Income Ratio", "format": "Num (4)"}, {"reference": "SP-I-46", "reference_concat": "spi46", "type of data": "SP & SPA", "description": "Gross Annual Income Only populated if Income Estimation and Verification package is requested. Family Economic Unit Income. For Bronze this will hold the same value as SP-N-89. For Gold and Silver this will be a combination of supplied income and income estimates.", "offset": "Income", "format": "Num (8)"}, {"reference": "SP-I-47", "reference_concat": "spi47", "type of data": "SP & SPA", "description": "Revolving Credit Commitments as a % of Net Monthly Income Only populated if Income Estimation and Verification package is requested. (SP) Monthly credit commitments (revolving credit) divided by Net Monthly Income x 100 (Net Monthly Income is calculated from SP-I-46)", "offset": "Income Ratio", "format": "Num (4)"}, {"reference": "SP-I-48", "reference_concat": "spi48", "type of data": "SP & SPA", "description": "Non-Revolving Credit Commitments as a % of Net Monthly Income Only populated if Income Estimation and Verification package is requested. (SP) Monthly credit commitments (non revolving credit) divided by Net Monthly Income x 100 (Net Monthly Income is calculated from SP-I-46)", "offset": "Income Ratio", "fo